A Range: Student demonstrates excellence in practice with a focus on learning-focused culture.
B Range: Student demonstrates strong practice and inquiry into learning-focused culture.
C Range: Student demonstrates competent practice and inquiry learning-focused culture.
Not Achieved: Student does not demonstrate competent practice and/or inquiry into learning-focused culture.

A Range: Student demonstrates excellent practice within curriculum areas and in the wider school community.
B Range: Student demonstrates strong curriculum and community practice.
C Range: Student demonstrates competent curriculum and community practice.
Not Achieved: Student does not demonstrate competent curriculum and/or community practice.
Student does not demonstrate competent practice.
